name: AQUAMAX EMOILENT CREAM - 100G
FCUK HIM EAU DE TOILETTE SPRAY - 100ML
description:
At the heart of FCUK Him lies a dynamic blend of invigorating citrus and spicy notes, creating a scent that is both refreshing and exhilarating. The fragrance opens with a burst of zesty mandarin and tangy bergamot, evoking a sense of energy and vitality. As the scent develops, aromatic herbs and spices, such as basil and cardamom, emerge, adding depth and complexity to the composition. Finally, a base of warm woods and musk creates a lasting impression of masculinity and sophistication.

Perfect for everyday wear, FCUK Him Eau de Toilette Spray is versatile and charismatic, making it ideal for any occasion, from casual outings to special events. Whether you're heading to the office or enjoying a night out with friends, this fragrance leaves a lasting impression, exuding confidence and charm.

Housed in a sleek and modern bottle adorned with the iconic FCUK logo, Him is a symbol of contemporary style and individuality. Its bold design and distinctive aesthetic make it a standout addition to any fragrance collection, embodying the spirit of modern masculinity.

Indulge in the captivating scent of FCUK Him Eau de Toilette Spray and experience the essence of modern masculinity. With its invigorating aroma and confident charm, this fragrance will become your signature scent, a reflection of your unique personality and individuality. Embrace your bold spirit with FCUK Him and make every moment extraordinary.
